<h3>Building a Weekly AI Traffic Dashboard</h3>
<p>For ongoing monitoring, save your exploration report and check it weekly. Here is the weekly review process:</p>
<ol>
<li>Open your saved AI Traffic exploration</li>
<li>Check total AI sessions versus the previous week</li>
<li>Note any new AI sources that appeared (platforms change referrer domains)</li>
<li>Review the top 5 AI landing pages for changes</li>
<li>Check conversion rate from AI traffic versus your site average</li>
