</ol>
<p>The weekly review takes 10 minutes. Over time, the data reveals which content investments drive AI traffic and which do not. Pages that consistently appear as top AI landing pages should get priority for <a href="/blog/update-old-blog-posts/">content updates</a> and <a href="/blog/on-page-seo-guide/">on-page optimization</a>.</p>
<p>This data also feeds into your broader <a href="/blog/content-marketing-strategy/">content marketing strategy</a>. If AI platforms consistently cite your comparison pages but ignore your how-to guides, that signals what format AI engines prefer for your topic area. Publish more of what AI cites.</p>
